// jake's JakeScape  autospawner
// feel free to change the item id




program Autospawner;  //for private server
Const
//---------Setup----------//
Whatpickup1 ='::pickup 4444 1'; //What do you want to pickup?
Whatpickup2 ='::pickup 1111 1'; //What do you want to pickup?

Whatpickup8 ='::pickup 4172 1'; //What do you want to pickup?
Whatpickup9 ='::pickup 3210 1'; //What do you want to pickup?
Whatpickup10 ='::pickup 2345 1'; //What do you want to pickup?
Whatpickup11 ='::pickup 0398 100000000'; //What do you want to pickup?
WhoMade1 ='this auto is made by jake owner of jakescape XD'; //made by
Whatbank1 ='::bank'; //to change note sea turtle to real
WaitTime = 100000000000000; //so it dont restart
//-----------------------//

Procedure click;
Begin
clickmouse(255, 141,true); //click moparscape,
end;

Procedure Talk;
Begin
SendKeys(whatpickup1 + chr (13));
wait(1000)
SendKeys(whatpickup2 + chr (13));
wait(1000)
SendKeys(whatpickup3 + chr (13));
wait(1000)
SendKeys(whatpickup4 + chr (13));
wait(1000)
SendKeys(whatpickup5 + chr (13));
wait(1000)
SendKeys(whatpickup6 + chr (13));
wait(1000)
SendKeys(whatpickup7 + chr (13));
wait(1000)
SendKeys(whatpickup8 + chr (13));
wait(1000)
SendKeys(whatpickup9 + chr (13));
wait(1000)
SendKeys(whatpickup10 + chr (13));
wait(1000)
SendKeys(whatpickup11 + chr (13));
wait(1000)
SendKeys(whomade1 + chr (13));
wait(1000)
SendKeys(whatbank1 + chr (13));
end;


Begin
click;
wait (1000)
repeat
Talk;
Wait (WaitTime + random(50))
until(false)
end.

I touched it up a bit so it does all of the pickups and clicks on the moparscape window. (you may need to change the coords… i have a widescreen laptop so i have wierd coords lol.
